<br>
It's not critical right now but anyone that has anything to do with Shamen know how infuriating and limiting a lack of definition for your class can be, so they need to stop it before it get's too bad.<br>
<br>
Three minor changes I'd like to see are: <br>
<br>
1) Increased range on our dmg chant to put it in line with the increased Paladin range (the same could be offered to the Wardens for there dmg chant, for which they won't care about seeing as they all use bubble instead).<br>
<br>
2) The introducation of the triple resist chants that Paladins get. I gather they stack with the standard ones, so if it's consedered too powerful for a skald to have both, they should loose the single ones and just have the triple ones. I think we'd all be happy with that seeing as we've been asking for it for ages anyway.<br>
<br>
3) FoG changed to an 8 pt realm skill (at the least, perhaps even lower) and it's ranged increased substantially so at least your group is gauranteed to get it's benifit even if they are spread out. Perhaps it could even have it's range removed seeing as it is on such a long timer. It'd be nice if the skill lasted longer, did more damage and had a shorter re-cast, but I'm going for bare minimum here and the price and range of effect are things that should be easy to change.<br>
<br>
I can't see anyone being able to say anything credible against these changes, which is why I limited the suggestion to just these. Once these were in things could be re-assesed again. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/ufenrisfil.showPublicProfile?language=EN>fenrisfil</A> at: 9/20/02 4:38:51 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c2a2><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/ukjeld.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kjeld</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Team Skald Contributor</span><br>  Posts: 79<br> <font color=#ff0000>(9/20/02 7:42:22 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=302.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Hmmm</span><hr size=1> Speaking of FOG, I have an idea that could make it quite a bit more usefull. <br>
Make it a song with normal song range, but not group only. That mean, every ally close to the skald would benefit from it. It will really shine in all of the big open field battles. I don't know if it is technically feasible, but for an expensive, short duration, long recast ability, heh ... <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><br><font color=#ff0000>- </font><a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/bteamskald>Team Skald</a><font color=#ff0000> - </font><a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1>General Discussion</a><font color=#ff0000> - </font> <!-- #EndEditable -->
